Randall is an AI/ALife mouse written in Python.  The directory called
alife_randall is an svn repository that I used periodically to check
in my work.  The checkout is just the latest revision of that repository
for quick access.

Randall is GPL V2 or greater and was written my me (Joseph Lewis <joehms22@gmail.com>)
while on winter break from the University of Denver 2010-2011.

Today is: 2011/01/13

