r6 | joseph | 2011-01-06 22:23:28 -0700 (Thu, 06 Jan 2011) | 3 lines

Added the ability to choose which actor the currently displayed statistics are for.  Safer handling and general cleanup of all site pages that needed to be actor-dynamic.

Removed world generation code from webserver and placed it in the index page.  In doing so a bug was fixed where a new world was generated for *every* new index page, causing hundreds of threads to be opened and hung.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5 | joseph | 2011-01-06 19:43:07 -0700 (Thu, 06 Jan 2011) | 18 lines

logos.py
Added a generic search mode to logos, that way events are easy to generate and add to actors.  The default mode seeks items associated with the current need finds the closest and goes there.
The explore mode now interacts with the items on the square it was initialized with.

Randall.py
About sixty lines cut out of randall by using the new generic mode.

world.py
Update the Actor's map every time it moves.

mapper.py
Changed some test cases.

map.py
Removed a line that was printing out a variable, messing up output.

actor_map.py
Displays the internal map for an actor.
